{
  "stem": "5740.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was hearing all the time about the pogroms here, pogroms there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never occurred a pogrom in Bedzin, but I was scared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Bedzin, there were, as I told you, there were a few doctors, non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was most probably some solicitors non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were caretakers non-Jewish and, you know, servants non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were maybe a few shops non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on Saturday, you felt it in every corner that it's Shabbos, because everything was closed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last-- we lived at first, when I was a little girl-- we really didn't live so comfort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I tell you, most probably from 1934 how we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a huge, what you call here, a unit, that belonged to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole house belongs to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The magistrate of the city was out tenant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was in the same house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a beautiful room, all in pink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it must have been big, because there was a piano in that room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a beautiful couch in that room, which was like my bed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a round table, with chairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a desk which, when I turned it, it became, like, like, my makeup cabinet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a big, big wardrobe and-- and a big oven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to have a [INAUDIBLE] oven, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Ah, for heating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For heating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was Jewish, one was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One who was cooking was Jewish and one who was-- but not always.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes we had only one non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was cooking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was helping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But mostly, we had two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was always friends with every servant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not really, friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
